quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  22,65,"Ese ntubona ko Allah yategetse ibiri mu isi kubacira bugufi ndetse ko n’amato agenda mu nyanja ku bw’itegeko rye? Anafashe ikirere kugira ngo kitagwa ku isi uretse igihe azabishakira. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Nyirimpuhwe bihebuje, akaba na Nyirimbabazi ku bantu"
  22,66,"Ni na We wabahaye ubuzima hanyuma akazabubambura (igihe cyo gupfa), maze akazabubasubiza (ku munsi w’imperuka). Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ni indashima"
  22,67,"Buri muryango w’abantu (Umat) twawuhaye imigenzo bagomba gukurikiza (mu kugaragira n’indi mihango y’idini). Bityo, (abahakanyi) ntibazakugishe impaka kuri iryo hame, ahubwo ujye ubahamagarira kugana Nyagasani wawe. Mu by’ukuri wowe (Muhamadi) uri mu muyoboro ugororotse (idini rya Isilamu)"
  22,68,"Kandi nibaramuka bakugishije impaka, ujye uvuga uti “ Allah ni We uzi neza ibyo mukora.”"
  22,69,Allah azabakiranura ku munsi w’imperuka ku byo mutavugagaho rumwe
  22,70,Ese ntuzi ko Allah azi ibiri mu kirere no ku isi byose? Mu by’ukuri ibyo byose biri mu gitabo (kirinzwe). Mu by’ukuri ibyo kuri Allah biroroshye
  22,71,"Kandi bagaragira ibindi bitari Allah, atigeze abahera gihamya ndetse batanafitiye ubumenyi. Kandi ababangikanyamana ntibazagira umutabazi"
  22,72,"Kandi iyo basomewe amagambo yacu asobanutse, ubona mu buranga bw’abahakanye (hagaragaramo) kutayishimira, bari hafi gusumira ababasomera amagambo yacu! Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ese mbabwire ibibi birusha ibyo? Ni umuriro Allah yasezeranyije ba bandi bahakanye, kandi iryo ni ryo herezo ribi.”"